{"tid":1335203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<721遊行Q&A>  民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:13:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4261c33e6f081989da4c1f5d36c29ab920d2a675","tid":1335203,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n&lt;721遊行Q&amp;A&gt;<br />\n<br />\n明天遊行終點在哪裡？<br />\n－上訴委員會已裁決維持灣仔盧押道作為遊行終點的決定，因此民陣只能按不反對通知書，到盧押道結束遊行。<br />\n<br />\n民陣到達終點後會有什麼安排？<br />\n－我們會嚴格按照不反對通知書要求，在終點只會盡力宣佈「立即解散」。<br />\n<br />\n如果人流太多，加入遊行的人流倒灌到灣仔，終點安排會否有困難？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n到盧押道後，如何離開灣仔？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n如果灣仔地鐵站不能疏散，所有巴士又停開，怎麼辦？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n如果書展人流、中途參與遊行人流、離開遊行的人流相沖，怎麼辦？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n如果我需要向金鐘離開，又是否可行？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n如果灣仔港鐵站因為人流太多而「飛站」，又可以如何離開？<br />\n－請向警察查詢。<br />\n<br />\n如果明天遊行路線以外，有％＆＄％＃<br />\n－總之，請向警察查詢。警方可以施加上述安排，我們必須相信警方有能力可以處理。<br />\n<br />\n#唔係曲 #點會曲 #我哋係真心嘅<br />\n#萬物都向警察查詢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67153943_2366502206730490_3996592645181800448_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQnUucqCXvVQGkpvyNIy0uZuO-UurZregg_jM2-6kQ_maNPO4E8n8D3iigQYqApUb_M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=cc5f99ce1129197cc5f2973e754c83fa&amp;oe=5DBA8B83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67153943_2366502206730490_3996592645181800448_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQnUucqCXvVQGkpvyNIy0uZuO-UurZregg_jM2-6kQ_maNPO4E8n8D3iigQYqApUb_M%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dcc5f99ce1129197cc5f2973e754c83fa%26oe%3D5DBA8B83&h=3f7c2f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2366502203397157/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2366502203397157%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4hzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=3bab1b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2366502203397157/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"f6c05c71d36f0953fe547aed41d39e1f44a33219","tid":1335203,"uid":212626,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"民陣今次堅嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e804948e538738249eb9031fbc5da51c5671ab3","tid":1335203,"uid":192787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"721721"},{"pid":"78b13ef1c930e201d89a1706707b3f31bc74d3d5","tid":1335203,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 大家有無諗過呢場抗爭既end game係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7e1f446301e6b614c3936c1855897eb8cc13bdf","tid":1335203,"uid":54921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ea6faa9da2b6879d0aea5a76b74a478a9cc6d6","tid":1335203,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"去到修頓又要回頭搭地鐵? 但後面啲人都湧緊黎點返轉頭?<br />\n<br />\n官逼民反，大陸總係有打壓人民既心。<br />\n<br />\n林奠，條條人命死傷都算到你頭上，你覺得主會原諒你，上天會原諒你?"},{"pid":"5cfcff65f0f06b24c0eb424e7cce0ef952af8749","tid":1335203,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"市民不滿想問候警察家人可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n請向警察查詢<br />\n<br />\n<code>1）有人講咗「唔好再覆」就唔好爭住屌一毛、恥笑一毛，亦唔好跟住留「唔好再覆」，否則等同推po。2）俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。3）新聞po睇日期先覆，小心一毛伎倆：有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po。最後，721去遊行！</code>"},{"pid":"4768de60677d71a8fecb72178a654